	* config/h8300/h8300.md: Likewise.

@@ -686,14 +686,14 @@ struct cum_arg
 
    H8/300
 	      vvvv context
-   1 0000 7900xxxx 		mov.w	#0x1234,r3

 	      ^^^^ function
 
    H8/300H
 	      vvvvvvvv context
-   2 0000 7A00xxxxxxxx 		mov.l	#0x12345678,er3

 	    ^^^^^^ function

@@ -97,7 +97,7 @@
